name: #2 DELONG: Dragon Descendant.
description: Meet Delong, a flying dog with a quirky personalities. Delong has been hiding from the face of the earth since a long long time ago because of his bad experience being hunted down by bad humans. Now he's on a mission, there are rumours spreading around about his offspring. People believe Delong are dragon descendants. Cop this artwork, spread it and help Delong to find his dragon parents!
